ty-love\/","url_meta":{"origin":26563,"position":2},"title":"Hasan on Akhlaq: Good character is generosity, charity, love","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 9, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Washa\u2019 reported: Hasan al-Basri, may Allah have mercy on him, was asked about good character and he said, \u201cIt is generosity, charitable giving, and loving kindness towards people.\u201d Source: al-Muwasha\u0304 1\/28 \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u0648\u0634\u0627\u0621 \u0642\u0627\u0644 \u0633\u064f\u0626\u0650\u0644 \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0633\u0646 \u0639\u0646 \u062d\u064f\u0633\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u062e\u064f\u0644\u0642 \u0641\u0642\u0627\u0644 \u0627\u0644\u0643\u0631\u0645 \u0648\u0627\u0644\u0628\u0630\u0644\u0629 \u0648\u0627\u0644\u062a\u0651\u064e\u0648\u062f\u0651\u064f\u062f \u0625\u0644\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0633 1\/28 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0648\u0634\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0638\u0631\u0641 \u0648\u0627\u0644\u0638\u0631\u0641\u0627\u0621","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":30709,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/05\/22\/fudayl-spend-time-hasan-al-khuluq\/","url_meta":{"origin":26563,"position":3},"title":"Fudayl on Company: Spend time with those having good character","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 22, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Nu\u2019aym reported: Fudayl ibn \u2018Iyad, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cIf you mix with people, mix with those who have good character; it only invites to good. Do not mix with those who have bad character, for it only invites to evil.\u201d Source: H\u0323ilyat al-Awliya\u0304' 11728 \u0639\u0646\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u063